Grid Search

Pipeline

{% raw %} 
def create_pipeline(
    num_features: int, add_pca: bool = True, pca_n_components: int = 50
) -> Pipeline:
    """Create and return pipeline"""

    preprocessor = []

    preprocessor.append(
        ColumnTransformer(
            (
                "ohe",
                OneHotEncoder(handle_unknown="ignore"),
                slice(num_features - 1),
            )  # slice indicating all cols
        )
    )
    if add_pca:
        preprocessor.append(("pca", PCA(pca_n_components)))

    pipe = Pipeline(
        steps=[("preprocessor", preprocessor), ("classifier", "passthrough")]
    )
    return pipe
